 There is no limit on the number of exchanged exchange elements between lst1 and lst2.
If it is possible to exchange elements component between the lst1 and lst2 to make reach 
 all the elements of lst1 to be even, return " YES ". 
 Otherwise, return " NO ".
For example:
exchange({1, 2, 3, 4}, {1, 2, 3, 4}) => "YES"
exchange({1, 2, 3, 4}, {1, 5, 3, 4}) => "NO"
